{"tid":732486,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉石籬非禮4夜歸女   警拘巴裔魁梧疑犯   張超雄：政府應撥2億支援南亞裔","createTime":"2018-07-07T03:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T03:35:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5d28e44b8626a936ce2c38147d53e79ad5e4b2","tid":732486,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180707/s00046/6871cd2202278321d33059f6a67d916c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180707%2Fs00046%2F6871cd2202278321d33059f6a67d916c.jpg&h=34f2118d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180707/s00002/1530901736304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180707%2Fs00002%2F1530901736304&d=6vf7gazgAu9I%2B1pFCTXgp5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=d625680c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180707%2Fs00002%2F1530901736304&h=b8fe54d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180707/s00002/1530901736304</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】葵涌石籬邨在上月22日起發生4宗風化案，夜歸女途人遭摸臂摸胸或非禮。警方昨日拘捕一名土生土長、在邨內居住及就讀中學的17歲巴基斯坦裔男子，相信與案有關，並在其寓所檢出相信是犯案時所穿的衣物。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨午5時在葵涌石籬邨拘捕17歲巴裔男子，涉與區內多宗非禮案有關，押返其石籬邨其寓所搜證。葵青警區刑事總督察姚永勤表示，在涉案男子家中檢獲證物，包括疑似是案發時所穿衣服，相信該男子涉及上月22日起區內4宗非禮案。疑犯昨被警拘留調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查發現，僅17歲的疑犯就讀中學，土生土長，為本港永久居民，與家人同住該邨，相信他獨行犯案，在4案中侵犯獨行夜歸、年齡介乎20至35歲的受害人。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方在接報後十分重視此案，翻查大量閉路電視片段，再配合受害人詳細口供資料，至昨日鎖定疑犯身分，並派探員扮街坊在疑犯所住大廈的大堂等候，以便在他出門時拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方強調，不容非禮行為，呼籲如同區有同類案件受害人，挺身報警，巿民如有與案相關資料，可致電3661 2941與葵青區重案組第二隊聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180703/20438837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F20438837&d=6vf7gazgAu9I%2B1pFCTXgp5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=d26793c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F20438837&h=a27b5520\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180703/20438837</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160403/photo/0403-00176-091h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160403%2Fphoto%2F0403-00176-091h1.jpg&h=8b8a11a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工黨立法會議員張超雄指勞工處有就業大使提供協助，「有好過無」，但絕非良策。他籲港府撥出至少2億元，為少數族裔提供繙譯等支援，向僱主提供更多聘請誘因。"},{"pid":"3d6672c5b2d96cb85471facadecfa99c4f5277c9","tid":732486,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"班蝻開始黎料<br />\n遲下有老強新聞都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c818608b71278eb347c643c712100847ced8ea","tid":732486,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d6672c5b2d96cb85471facadecfa99c4f5277c9","tid":732486,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"班蝻開始黎料<br />\n遲下有老強新聞都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀夜晚成日都有蝻聯群結黨, 當街圍港女抱走去啦<br />\n<br />\n唔係新鮮事"},{"pid":"3599edb5fb356c4de97f92f9998aea94d87e47ef","tid":732486,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"港女都係臭雞 岩晒"},{"pid":"fba2b1fda4d005578e50e2764b1f456cdb8ebf8a","tid":732486,"uid":76471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班蝻開始黎料<br />\n遲下有老強新聞都唔出奇[img]assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n瞓咗幾耐？"}]}